Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy for the people to hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but the truth often isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- You got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Coming to us live\Nand now speaking to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- In the estate where\Nformer White Fang leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've seen it and she's\Nalways looked out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you all for assembling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to take time to\Naddress some of the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been circulating\Naround our island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that it is important\Nfor the people of this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,territory to understand the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you feel\Nabout the human race,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can all agree\Nthat the event now known as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Fall of Beacon was a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A tragedy that will set both\Nman and Faunus-kind back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,While the main aggressor is still unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we do have official\Nconfirmation that Adam Taurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the leader of a powerful\Nsplinter group working inside the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,White Fang, was partially\Nresponsible for these attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His actions not only\Ntarnished the reputation of an
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,organization originally\Ncreated to bring peace
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and equality to all,\Nbut to our entire race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With each day that this\Nman remains unpunished,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes increasingly\Ndifficult to condemn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,those that look down upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, a spy from\Nthe same splinter group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,set their sights on this very home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My own daughter, Blake,\Nand her friend did their
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,very best to apprehend this individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,While they were unsuccessful\Nafter being physically
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,assaulted and seriously injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they were successful in\Nobtaining the assailant's Scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we have been able\Nto ascertain that Adam Taurus
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,has plans to overthrow the\Ncurrent leader of the White Fang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sienna Khan, and take\Nover the reins himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His radical plans do not stop\Nthere, the documents on this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,scroll proclaim his next target to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,be Haven Academy and\Nits attached CCT Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Their plan is to strike on\Nthe last full moon before the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning of the Fall semester,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,roughly two months from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sent my swiftest\Nmessenger to the government of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistral, but I believe we\Nhave a greater responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My relationship with the White Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has been an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Years ago, I led the\Norganization to help try
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and create a world where I,\Nand every Faunus who wished,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,could walk alongside the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I believe we made\Ngreat strides toward this goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it was made clear to me\Nthat the people both in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of the White Fang\Nwanted faster results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I stepped down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sienna Khan was\Nappointed as my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I do not fully\Ncondone many of her methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do condone is\Nwhat Sienna fights for:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea that the Faunus and humans are,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and should be, equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam Taurus does not seem\Nto have that goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What he has done benefits\Nno one but himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time that the Faunus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,showed the world that we are equals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Time that we snuff out\Nthis splinter group,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and restore the White\NFang to what it once was!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To do this, I think the answer is clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we must go to Haven and\Nprotect it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we proceed any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to invite my daughter\Nto come and share her story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only as a former\Nmember of the White Fang,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but also as a survivor\Nof the Fall of Beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ilia] Traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything the\Nhumans have done to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,everything they've put us through,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you're asking us to help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know we haven't been treated fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where was their help when the Dust
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,companies treated our people like slaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was their help when Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hunted Faunus just for being who they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was my help when my parents
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,were killed in a Dust mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Young lady, progress takes\Npatience and cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Belladonnas are\Nthe worse kind of Faunus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us to work with the same people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that are trying to hold us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you truly, truly want\Nto help your people now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is the time to support\NAdam, not the Belladonnas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He will bring about the\Nfuture that you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you are unwilling to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,know that the White\NFang will do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Sun] Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] Did he age backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jaune] He's possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ren] Or reincarnated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Oh, isn't it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is very weird, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all just take a second and remember
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is very\Noverwhelming for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just I've never really met
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huntsmen and Huntresses before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, uh, we've never met\Na person with two souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first times all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not to break up the whole\Ngetting-to-know-you game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need to have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind showing us your\Nlittle parlor trick, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I'll still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is so very good to\Nsee you again, students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Professor Ozpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And though I may be the one speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar is still present mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's merely handed over\Nthe control, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar Voiceover] Just don't make us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm afraid this all\Nmust be very perplexing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- And alarming, and bizarre,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and just really kind of\Nhard to believe overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's good to see you children
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,still have your sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've all been through\Ntremendous hardship already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- I mean, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you once that I made\Nmore mistakes than any man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,woman, and child on this planet,\Nand I wasn't exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For thousands of years, I've\Nwalked the surface of Remnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,living, dying, and reincarnating
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the body of a like-minded soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Professor Ozpin you all\Nmet was not my first form,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and clearly wasn't my last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an extraordinarily strenuous
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,process on everyone involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- So who, what, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am the combination of\Ncountless men who've spent their
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,lives trying to protect\Nthe people of Remnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With every rebirth, my soul\Nis eventually merged with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,another and I am changed,\Nbut my memories stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This curse was bestowed\Nupon me by the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because I failed to\Nstop Salem in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must stop her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- And how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- We start by ensuring the\Nsafety of the Relic of Knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, well, well, look who's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, I never thought\NI'd see a Schnee in this camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Vernal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't normally deal\Nin trafficking people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,not really worth our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, once we realized we\Nhad a Schnee, that changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're going to ransom me\Nback to my father, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's a shame you're a Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd probably do quite well around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] I would never\Nsink to your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just keep quiet and cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be back in your\Nmansion before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make this complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going to make this\Ncomplicated is when my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,finds out I didn't make it to Mistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know my sister, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Operative of the Atlas Military?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in Mistral now, and\Nwhen she hears I'm missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't take her long\Nto find me, and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I don't know if\Nit's more funny or sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're clearly out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister isn't in Mistral anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No Atlas personnel are in Mistral anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,General Ironwood closed the\Nborders and recalled all of his
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,little troops and tin cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is coming to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We were stuck at a dead end, but now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we can just take little cute boy Ozpin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to Lionheart and have\Nhim set things straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're not sure that's the best idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I thought the headmasters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all took their orders from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- That was the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Four lieutenants I can trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,especially during times of reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But Qrow told me about\Nyour meeting with Leonardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't just behaving irrationally,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he's disobeying specific\Ninstructions I had left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to jump to conclusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't want to rule out\Nany possibilities, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No one outside of this\Nroom knows that I've paired
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with Oscar, and I think it may\Nbe best to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Play things close to the chest\Nuntil we get a better hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we have two steps ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is enlisting\Nthe aid of more Huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- But the Mistral council--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Doesn't own every\NHuntsman in the Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been here enough times
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to know where we can find some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin] So long as they're trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can trust them\Nto put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw together a list tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- After that, we can move on to step two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's step two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Getting you four into fighting shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, uh, we already know how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can only fight so long\Nas you have Crescent Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still lacking\Nin hand-to-hand combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Arc, I'm glad to\Nhear you've improved,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but sorry to say, you've yet\Nto unlock your Semblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you still have a-ways\Nto go before you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to pose any real threat\Nagainst Salem and her forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And though Oscar can give\Nme temporary control,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll need to strengthen\Nhis body and his Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar Voiceover] Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- He'll inherit my muscle memory in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but practice will expedite the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- But if Qrow's out looking for Huntsmen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then who's going to teach us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I believe I was the\Nheadmaster of Beacon Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have approximately one month
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,before classes resume at Haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If Salem were to plan an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it would make sense that it occur
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to students' return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much time, but\Nit's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't expect me to go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've gotta be kidding me.
